snippet.textDisplay: The referee was catastrophic, he made few crucial mistakes, for me busquets should have been sent of already in first half, fekir unfair red card, arguably penalty on arthur and I just can't understand how he didn't see bartra's foul on messi. Great match though, as a Barca fan I really enjoy attacking football but their defense, not only defenders but whole team are so desoriented when they lose the ball, they really need to improve playing without the ball. I hope it'll get better because stronger teams will punish them for their mistakes.
